dialogue("Abby", "WHAT!? WHERE AM I?", 0.3, c_white, global.fonteNormal, -1)
dialogue("", "The heat hits you first dry, suffocating warmth that clings to your skin like a second layer.", 0.3, c_aqua, global.fonteNormal, -1)
dialogue("Abby", "This isn't my room... This is nowhere I've ever been.", 0.3, c_white, global.fonteNormal, -1)
dialogue("", "You're standing on a weathered stone wall. Below, a vast desert stretches endlessly under a pale sun.", 0.3, c_aqua, global.fonteNormal, -1)
dialogue("Abby", "What happened to me? I lay down... I just wanted to sleep...", 0.3, c_white, global.fonteNormal, -1)
